    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is flawless! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
