    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and pampered with regular detailing. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. If you\u2019re looking for total perfection and a ride that's been loved, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 44500.0,
