    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and a comprehensive rod bearing service was recently completed to ensure long-term bottom-end integrity. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability the E46 is renowned for. The exterior finish is flawless, and the interior presents with virtually no wear on the Nappa leather bolsters, making this a true turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
